The paper discusses graph drawing and topology, which are common topics in computational geometry (cs.CG) and data structures (cs.DS). The use of interactive exploration functionalities suggests a focus on human-computer interaction (cs.SI), while the application of the approach to three datasets suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) or statistical analysis (cs.SD).
